page_title: Quickstart: Generate images with Azure OpenAI Service using PowerShell
page_description: Learn how to generate images with Azure OpenAI Service by using PowerShell and the endpoint and access keys for your Azure OpenAI resource.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription. Create one for free.- For this task, the latest version of PowerShell 7 is recommended because the examples use new features not available in Windows PowerShell 5.1.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the East US region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.
